WEBVTT

00:01.323 --> 00:02.405
You put him in a coma?

00:02.457 --> 00:04.207
Cryogenic sleep is more accurate.

00:04.242 --> 00:05.708
Welcome to management.

00:05.744 --> 00:07.994
Even if I had the footage
of the things that happened

00:08.045 --> 00:09.295
in your home, Tom, I truly doubt

00:09.331 --> 00:10.330
you'd wanna see it.

00:12.334 --> 00:13.466
Who's Edgar L. Abbot?

00:13.501 --> 00:15.385
I don't know. But we need to find him.

00:15.420 --> 00:17.470
Good, we are all here.

00:17.505 --> 00:20.089
You bought a gun to kill Arthur.

00:22.344 --> 00:24.010
I'm a better person than them.

00:24.062 --> 00:25.144
Charlie...

00:25.180 --> 00:26.346
Aaugh!

00:26.348 --> 00:29.432
Ohhhh!

